# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Include the following.
!LICENSE.md
!README.md
!config.schema.json
!dist/**
!package.json
!src/**

# Ship the source alongside dist so the emitted declaration maps (.d.ts.map) and source maps (.js.map) resolve to readable TypeScript - "go to definition" and debugger
# step-into land on the real source, and the masterclass-reference goal is served (consumers can read the source right in node_modules). The test scaffolding is the one
# part of src that earns no place in the published tarball.
src/**/*.test.ts
src/**/*.helpers.ts
src/**/*.fixtures.ts
